==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Negrita
<hw>Ne*gri"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp., blackish,
fem. of <ets>negrito</ets>, dim. of <ets>negro</ets> black.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A blackish fish (<spn>Hypoplectrus
nigricans</spn>), of the Sea-bass family. It is a native of the West
Indies and Florida.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Negritic</ent>⟦br⟧
